summary: Marvel Removes 'Captain Mar-Vell' Text From the Official Captain Marvel Site
title: Marvel Removes 'Captain Mar-Vell' Text From the Official Captain Marvel Site
body:
Marvel Removes ‘Captain Mar-Vell’ Text From the Official #CaptainMarvel Site

A couple of weeks ago, when Marvel launched their official Captain Marvel 90s-inspired site, some people noticed something very interesting with the animated GIF of Jude Law’s character.

If you looked at the alt-text of the image, it described the character as “Captain Mar-Vell”:

That has now been changed, and they removed the “Captain Mar-Vell” and replaced it with just “Kree”:

This isn’t the…

body:
RUMOR: Where Captain Marvel Was During Infinity War (Possible Spoilers)

Ever since Nick Fury paged Captain Marvel in the post-credit scene of Avengers: Infinity War, fans have been debating about where Carol Danvers was during the movie and why Fury didn’t call her earlier.

Now a new rumor from the Captain Marvelmovie may explain it, and it’s really not as surprising as some people have speculated over the last year. But first, it’s good to look back at the official…
